        public static int SpreadsheetView_cellFont

        This symbol is the offset where the R.attr.cellFont attribute's value can be found in the SpreadsheetView array.

        May be a reference to another resource, in the form "@[+][package:]type:name" or to a theme attribute in the form "?[package:][type:]name".
